{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":30}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"算术奇观","authors":["胡长益"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：听说您对数学很有研究。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：好说。不过比起数学家华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗庚教授，我还差那么一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：嘿，倒挺谦虚的。今儿个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要向您请教个问题。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：不敢当。您是要问小代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数、大代数，还是解析几"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何、立体几何、微积分？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：不不！太深奥了我不懂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要问的是算术题：一加"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一等于多少？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：啊！就这个？我向你提出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗议！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：怎么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我又不是幼儿园的小孩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问这种问题，纯粹是对我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的污辱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：这问题简单哪？你就答不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：别唬人，一加一难道不等"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于二？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：错了。我问你，一只鞋加"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只鞋是几双鞋？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：两双！……不，是一双。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：一丈布加一尺布是几尺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：是十一尺布。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：还是的。这一加一就偏偏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不等于二嘛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：你这不是算术。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：我再问你个减法。四减一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是多少？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：让我想一想，其中一定又"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有奥妙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：喂，想好了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：好了。按照你的“神机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妙算”，四减一不等于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三，而是等于七或是三十"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：为什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：四双鞋减一只鞋还有七只"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞋；四丈布减一尺布还有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十九尺布。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：可惜，这道题你又吃了鸭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：那等于几？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：等于五，或者零。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：啊？等于五那不成了四加"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：你这是颠倒是非。就说眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前这张桌子，有四个角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把它砍掉一个角……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：还有三个角。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：亏你对数学还有研究呢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你仔细数数。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：咦，是五个角，不假。可"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么又等于零呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：你瞧，那树上有四只鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我“砰”的一枪打掉了一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只，还有几只？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：那三只也吓飞了，一只也"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：那不等于零吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：你这是歪理，哪里是算术"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：我再问你个乘法。你看过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《马克辛三部曲》吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：看过。怎么？这乘法跟电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"影还有关系？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：有。那些资产阶级银行家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向马克辛提出二乘二等于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几的问题，那是无理取闹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我经过精心的研究，发现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了一个新的答案，二乘二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以等于三。你信不信？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我——不信。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：好。我问你，两个两父子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是几个人？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：四个人呀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：不对。你和你父亲是两父"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子；你父亲和你祖父又是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两父子。这两个两父子是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几个人？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：这……是三个人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：所以二乘二等于三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：有你的。现在还剩下个除"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"法了。你要是能证明四除"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以二不等于二，这数学家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就让您当了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：一言为定。咱们加加倍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我给你算个八除以二不等"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于四，而等于零。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：合乎逻辑吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：当然。算术里那个8字怎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"么写？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：上面一个0，下面一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"0，两个0叠罗汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：不错。八除以二，你就把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这8字拦腰一切，不就等"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于0了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：对。算术要照你这么算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用切，你也就等于0了。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}